    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Onychalges pachyspathus Gaud, 1968, larva. A—dorsal view; B—ventral view; C—leg I in ventral view; D—leg II in ventral view; E—genu-tarsus III in ventral view. Scale bars: 100 Μm = A, B; 50 Μm = C – E." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/252826/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.252827>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Onychalges pachyspathus Gaud, 1968, protonymph. A—dorsal view; B—ventral view; C—tibia-tarsus IV in ventral view. Scale bars: 100 Μm = A, B; 50 Μm = C." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/252827/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.252828>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Onychalges pachyspathus Gaud, 1968, tritonymph. A—dorsal view; B—ventral view; C—tarsus III in ventral view; D—tarsus IV in ventral view. Scale bars: 100 Μm = A, B; 50 Μm = C, D." ;
